## Implementation

**Type Checker Extension**
```typescript
pi.events.on('file:changed', async ({ path }) => {
  if (isTypeScriptFile(path)) {
    const errors = await tsc.checkFile(path);
    pi.events.emit('typecheck:result', { path, errors });
  }
});
```

**Linter Extension**
```typescript
pi.events.on('file:changed', async ({ path }) => {
  const warnings = await eslint.checkFile(path);
  pi.events.emit('lint:result', { path, warnings });
});
```

**UI Aggregator Extension**
```typescript
pi.events.on('typecheck:result', (data) => updatePanel('types', data));
pi.events.on('lint:result', (data) => updatePanel('lint', data));
pi.events.on('test:result', (data) => updatePanel('tests', data));
```
